{
  "stem": "8784.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And in those Aktions, they would take people, round them up, and bring them to, to some concentration camps, in many cases to Auschwitz or other similar camps, work, work camps where they were--",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They simply disappeared.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At the time, we would not know what was happening to the people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Rumors would have a lot of things, you know, that they were killed, that they were taken away, but we did not know any facts.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We did not have any idea, at least I didn't.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If there were some people in the ghetto-- there is a good chance that there were-- that knew a little more than I did as a youngster.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so this, this began to play a role in our psyche in living in the ghetto that we, we wouldn't know what the future holds for us.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "At that time, we, all of, all the eight of us were living in the, in the, basement room in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The-- sometime in 1942, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I happened to be in the street of the ghetto, in [NON-ENGLISH] when two small trucks with Germans came into the ghetto to round up some people for work.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Of course, we didn't know where, where those, where those people would be taken at that time because nobody had to bother explaining to you why they're loading you into a truck.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They simply loaded-- at that time it appeared that they loaded 100 of us into those two small pickups.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they were covered trucks.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I remember them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The, the SS guards appeared like spic and span, clean, quickly giving orders, shouting orders for, for those people they rounded up, they loaded on the trucks.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they took us out of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
